  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to develop a clinical protocol to detoxify patients from opiates
      to naltrexone using buprenorphine and to develop pilot data for a grant application for a
      controlled study of the efficacy of the new clinical protocol for outpatients.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
