  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

        Males/Females, ages 21-50. Opiate dependence according to DSM-IV criteria. Self-reported
        use within the last 30 days. Agreeable to conditions of study and signed informed consent.

        Exclusion Criteria:

        psychiatric disorder that requires medication therapy. History of seizures. Pregnant and/or
        nursing women. Dependent on etoh or benzodiazepines or other sedative-hypnotics. Acute
        hepatitis. Other medical conditions that deem participation to be unsafe.
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
